name: sdh-cross-repo-announce-read
description: >
  Use at session start to process unsolicited announcements that arrived from
  another repo — a client reads from its server, a parent server reads from its
  microservices (ANNOUNCE-NNN.md files in docs/server-announcements/ or
  docs/microservice-announcements/). Covers scanning the folders, integrating,
  acknowledging by deleting the file, and committing. To PUSH an announcement
